  <statement>
      
      <p>
          Let <m>X_1, X_2, Y</m> be independent random variables where <m>E(X_i)=17, Var(X_i)=6</m> and <m>E(Y)=30, Var(Y)=6</m>.
      </p>
      
      <p>
          Let <m>Z</m> be the random variable defined by: <me>Z= 5X_1-4X_2+3Y.</me>
      </p>
      
      
      <p>
